# EPSON Projector Setup

# Overview
This project demonstrates the setup and replacement process of an EPSON projector in a meeting room environment.

## Problem
The old projector was unable to display the screen properly.

# Diagnosis
- The old projector was overheating.
- The display cable was replaced, but the issue still persisted.

# Solution
Steps performed:
1. Replaced the old projector with a new EPSON projector.
2. Connected the display cable and power cord.
3. Adjusted the projector height and screen alignment.
4. Configured the display resolution to 4:3.

# Commands Used
N/A

# Result
The new projector was successfully installed and able to display the screen normally.

# Notes
This setup was performed for meeting room operational purposes.
